##Key Takeaways

The 3-Stage AI Funnel: Brand optimization happens in three phases. It starts with the Knowledge Panel (Bottom of funnel: establishing identity), moves to Credibility (Middle: proving you're the best option), and ends with AI Advocacy (Top: the AI actively recommending you to strangers researching your niche).

Realistic Timelines: Expect a 1-year timeline to fully optimize a personal brand. Corporate brands take about 2 years due to messier digital footprints and internal approval bottlenecks.

Assistive vs. Generative AI: The next major shift is AI moving from "generative" to "assistive." Engines won't just generate text; they will actively guide users to the best solution. Your goal is to train the AI to act as your pseudo-employee.

The 4-Step Execution Plan:
-Identify your core entities (who you are, who you serve, what problems you solve).
-Determine why you are credible and exactly how you can prove it.
-Publish that story on your "Entity Home" (your website's About page).
-Get the rest of the web to corroborate and agree with that story.